p = SomeMetaStep(SomeStep())
p.set_hyperparams_space(HyperparameterSpace({META_STEP_HP:
    RAND_INT_META_STEP, SOME_STEP_HP: RAND_INT_SOME_STEP}))
update_meta_step_hp_space = RandInt(0, 100)
p.update_hyperparams_space({META_STEP_HP: update_meta_step_hp_space})
assert p.hyperparams_space[META_STEP_HP] == update_meta_step_hp_space
assert p.wrapped.get_hyperparams_space()['somestep_hyperparam'
    ] == RAND_INT_SOME_STEP
